Hello,

We want to let you know that we are updating our FINAL FANTASY XIV User Agreement <https://link.square-enix-games.com/click/36559281.3423295/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdXBwb3J0LmV1LnNxdWFyZS1lbml4LmNvbS9ydWxlLnBocD9pZD01MzgzJmxhPTImdGFnPXVzZXJz/6220f2c6991c960233e0151fH76faf99d> for users on the 26 September 2024.

